						               													<description>It really makes you think! A game to challenge and inspire, getting you to stand in someone else's shoes while thinking outside the square as to how to solve daily dilemmas. Designed by Lesley Williams, this product is covered by Patent, Trade Mark and Copyright, and only available through TRUITY associated websites. The game is hilariously funny, yet astounding in its ability to move peoples perspective, getting people dealing with issues in constructive ways in just minutes. Deals with all areas of life, from environmental to social, to abuse, to financial decision, there are hundreds of questions in the pack and even blank cards so that you can write your own questions for others to answer. This product was designed to stimulate the creation of new neural pathways, and develop conscious choices, this product is being used in areas of family welfare, social welfare, hospitals, mental health hospitals, correctional facilities and more.A vanity press publication supporting a psychological counselling service.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;From the box:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A game to challenge and inspire.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The vision of Truity International is to inspire, mentor and facilitate people from all walks of life which includes health, peace and success.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Truity the game is a tool which leads people to develop enhanced thinking skills aligned with principles for ethical achievement. Play and enjoy.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
